### Global Leaderboard - Monthly
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/global?period=monthly&page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Category Leaderboard - Weekly (for category "science")
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/categories/science?period=weekly&page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### User Ranking Lookup (Authenticated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/leaderboards/users/me/rank?period=monthly&category=science
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>
